<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> pukaḷmātu viḷaṅka <hi rend="grantha">je</hi>yamātu virumpa nilamakaḷ vaḻara malarmakaḷ puṇara Urim<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> yil ciṟan=ta maṇimuṭi cūṭi mīṉavaṉ nilaikeṭa vi<supplied reason="omitted">l</supplied>lavar kulaitara vikkalar ciṅkaḻar melkaṭal pāyat tikkaṉaittum taṉ cakkara naṭātti vi<hi rend="grantha">jai</hi>yapi<hi rend="grantha">ṣē</hi>kam paṇṇi vira<hi rend="grantha">siṁ hāsa</hi> ṉattup puvaṉimuḻutuṭ<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> yāroṭum vīṟṟiruntaruḻiya kovirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>[ke<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>ripa]ṉmarāṉa cakkaravatti <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulottuṅkacoḷate
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vakku yāṇṭu <num value="28">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 8</num> Āvatu rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ppāṇṭināṭṭu muṭi(k)koṇṭacoḷavaḻanāṭṭuk kiḻkaḷakkūṟṟattu <hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi> yam keṅkaikoṇṭacoḻaccaruppetimaṅkalattu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kayyillāya(m) muṭ<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> yarkku poṉpaṟṟiuṭaiyāṉ ce<unclear>n</unclear>taṉ konampiyāṉa Atikaimāṉ v<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> tta tirununtāviḷak koṉṟukku viṭṭa cāvā muvāp perāṭu Aimpatum kaikkoṇṭu tevarkanmikaḷ vacam nittam Uḻakku ney Aḷakka<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭaveṉāṉeṉ Ivvūr Irukkum Āyaṉ villaruvikāṭaṉeṉ <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
</p>

